  <li>
    <p><a href="https://liutairan.github.io/projects/formation_control/"><strong>Multi-Agent System Formation Control</strong></a><br />
July 2016 - May 2020<br />
Developed new formation control methods, provided mathematical proofs.
Conducted numerical and experimental validation.</p>
